  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Gonfaloniere</span><br />Moreo Dagareon</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Gonfaloniere\" title=\"Gonfaloniere\">Gonfaloniere</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Moreo Dagareon</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a> <i><a href=\"/index.php/Gonfaloniere\" title=\"Gonfaloniere\">gonfaloniere</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Dagareon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Moreo was slain by his own elite guards in <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a> during the bloody power struggle in the city after the <a href=\"/index.php/Lysene_Spring\" title=\"Lysene Spring\">downfall</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">Rogare family</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Dagareon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" s